DTSTAMP:20260531T155620Z
DTSTART:20260603T120000Z
DTEND:20260603T132000Z
SUMMARY:🏒 Drop-In/Pickup – Ann Arbor
DESCRIPTION:35+ Drop-In Hockey\nRink: Biggby Ice Cube – Ann Arbor\n~3 mi from Ann Arbor\nPrice: $15\nIce: VAR Ann Arbor Ice Cube Varsity Rink\nSource: Bond Sports\nInfo: https://bondsports.co/org/246/262/schedule\nConfirm with rink — schedule subject to change.
